---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Gracias por suscribirte - Soy Bogart">
  <nav class="navbar">
    <div class="nav-content">
      <a href="/" class="logo">
        <img src="/assets/svg/LogoBogartWhite.svg" alt="Alberto Bogart" />
      </a>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="/#about">Trayectoria</a>
        <a href="/#blog">Blog</a>
        <a href="/#contact">Conozcamonos</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="thankyou">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="thankyou-card">
        <div class="checkmark">✓</div>
        <h1>¡Bienvenido a bordo!</h1>
        <p class="thankyou-subtitle">
          Gracias por suscribirte. A partir de ahora recibirás contenido exclusivo, 
          estrategias y herramientas directamente en tu bandeja de entrada.
        </p>
        <div class="thankyou-details">
          <p><strong>¿Qué sigue?</strong></p>
          <ul>
            <li>Revisa tu correo y confirma tu suscripción</li>
            <li>Recibirás un email de bienvenida con contenido exclusivo</li>
            <li>Semanalmente tendrás estrategias y novedades</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Volver al inicio</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="footer-content">
        <div class="footer-brand">
          <img src="/assets/svg/LogoBogartWhite.svg" alt="Alberto Bogart" />
          <p>Alberto Bogart - terapeuta de negocios 2026</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-bottom">
        <p>© 2026 Alberto Bogart. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>

<style>

  .navbar {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    background: #0600ff24;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);

    .nav-content {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .logo img {
      filter: brightness(0) invert(1);
      height: 40px;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2rem;

      a {
        color: var(--lighter);
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: color 0.3s ease;
        &:hover {
          color: var(--light);
        }
      }
    }
  }

  .thankyou {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 8rem 2rem 4rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .thankyou-card {
    max-width: 600px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
  }

  .checkmark {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    background: var(--brand-primary-light);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--dark);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--light);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-family: 'Exo', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .thankyou-subtitle {
    color: var(--lighter);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .thankyou-details {
    text-align: left;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;

    p {
      color: var(--brand-primary-light);
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;

      li {
        color: var(--lighter);
        padding: 0.4rem 0;
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
        position: relative;

        &::before {
          content: '→';
          position: absolute;
          left: 0;
          color: var(--brand-primary-light);
        }
      }
    }
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    background: var(--brand-primary);
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;

    &:hover {
      background: var(--brand-primary-light);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
  }

  .footer {
    padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);

    .footer-content {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .footer-brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;

      img {
        filter: brightness(0) invert(1);
        height: 40px;
      }

      p {
        color: var(--lighter);
      }
    }

    .footer-bottom {
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 2rem;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      p {
        color: var(--lighter);
        font-size: 0.875rem;
      }
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .navbar .nav-links {
      display: none;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
    }
    .thankyou-card {
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>